name: GIC,PLC-28D33B0:- Accessory, USB 2.0 Cable, Type A Male to B Male
leaf_category: Accessory for Converter Type A male to B Male
series_name: USB to RS232 / RS485 / RS422 Converter
description: PLC,Accessory for Converter 28A11A0, USB 2.0 Cable, Type A Male to B Male;-Compatible with USB 2.0*Input : USB 2.0 Protocol * Output : RS232 on DB9 Male connector compatible to PC RS485/RS422 on terminal block. * Communication Speed : 300bps to 230Kbps. * Auto direction control for RS485-2W data transmission. *Cable: USB 2.0 type A to type B cable.*Galvanic Isolation of 1.5kV *RS232/RS485 line protection: +/- 15kV ESD. *LED Indication for Transmit Receive signals. *Input power from USB port, no external power required. *2M enclosure with DIN Rail mounting. *Virtual COM port USB Drivers provided for Windows 7, 8, 8.1 and 10.
